<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 0.5em;"><b><a href="/wiki/Help:IPA" title="Help:IPA" class="mw-redirect">Pronunciation</a>:</b></td>
<td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 0.5em;"><span title="Pronunciation in IPA" class="IPA">[puɾtu'geʃ]&#160;(European), [portu'ges], [portu'geis] or [poʁtu'geiʃ]&#160;(Brazilian)</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="padding-left: 0.5em;">Spoken in:</td>
<td colspan="2" style="padding-left: 0.5em;">Natively in countries of <a href="/wiki/Africa" title="Africa">Africa</a>, <a href="/wiki/Europe" title="Europe">Europe</a>, <a href="/wiki/Asia" title="Asia">Asia</a> and <a href="/wiki/South_America" title="South America">South America</a>. Countries and territories with a significant percentage of speakers include <a href="/wiki/Andorra" title="Andorra">Andorra</a>, <a href="/wiki/Bermuda" title="Bermuda">Bermuda</a>, <a href="/wiki/Canada" title="Canada">Canada</a>, <a href="/wiki/France" title="France">France</a>, <a href="/wiki/Luxembourg" title="Luxembourg">Luxembourg</a> and <a href="/wiki/Jersey" title="Jersey">Jersey</a>.</td>
